content: I'm working on a research paper about sustainable business practices and I was wondering if you could help me find some relevant articles on eco-friendly cleaning products. By the way, I've been quite busy lately - I've been working on a group project for my Environmental Economics course with my classmates Rachel and Mike since April 1st, and we developed a sustainable business plan for a fictional company that produces eco-friendly cleaning products, so I'm already familiar with the topic.
